The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the removal of raindrops from images. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper uses a generative adversarial network (GAN) and visual attention, which are techniques commonly used in image processing and computer vision. Therefore, the paper could also belong to the graphics (cs.GR), multimedia (cs.MM), machine learning (cs.LG), or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
